log in to gcp console > press project name > new project > create it > change to new project
under APIs & Services > enable apis & service > +enable apis & service
search for YouTube Data API v3 > enable


under APIs & Services > credentials > +create credentials > api key
under APIs & Services > QAuth consent screen > external > create > fill app name +
user support email + Developer contact information > save and continue > add or remove scopes > add all scopes > update > save and continue 
> save and continue 
under APIs & Services > QAuth consent screen > testing > publish app > confirm

 under APIs & Services > credentials > +create credentials > Create OAuth client ID > desktop app >
create > ok


inside the python code folder make sure to remove   youtube_credentials.json if its there.


you need client id, secret and scopes for the code.


